    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31350.0,
      "end_time": 34670.0,
      "text": "I started my career 21 years ago in IT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34670.0,
      "end_time": 37190.0,
      "text": "but, actually, my love is in the sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39110.0,
      "end_time": 41800.0,
      "text": "I got to know many farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41800.0,
      "end_time": 45100.0,
      "text": "and the farmers shared their life with me, their passion,"
