    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46880.0,
      "end_time": 49700.0,
      "text": "and I decided that I wanted to be a farmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54540.0,
      "end_time": 57740.0,
      "text": "When I entered into this industry I thought to myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57740.0,
      "end_time": 61110.0,
      "text": "that, \"Hey, this is a opportunity to apply"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61110.0,
      "end_time": 63240.0,
      "text": "\"my engineering principles to farming.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64810.0,
      "end_time": 69300.0,
      "text": "For instance, when we bring in fish fries from the hatchery"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69300.0,
      "end_time": 73280.0,
      "text": "we have to count the fish and also check the fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73280.0,
      "end_time": 77300.0,
      "text": "Now previously, all this was done by estimation and by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77300.0,
      "end_time": 80230.0,
      "text": "but now we use a camera system"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80230.0,
      "end_time": 83350.0,
      "text": "to count the fish as they go past."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83350.0,
      "end_time": 85479.0,
      "text": "We can then also slow down the image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85480.0,
      "end_time": 87480.0,
      "text": "and then we can check the fish, as well."
