    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98750.0,
      "end_time": 101200.0,
      "text": "which is a Michelin-star restaurant in Singapore."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103770.0,
      "end_time": 105490.0,
      "text": "Our reputation is that we grow fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105490.0,
      "end_time": 108390.0,
      "text": "in as natural a way as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108400.0,
      "end_time": 111400.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why people like to buy from us."
